. (LAUGHS)  And he would do his calculations!  We did write up that.  Again, \'85 I can\rquote t remember what\rquote s happened to it. \'85 I did write something \'85 I wrote two or three articles for a publication }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 
