\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 \b\f39\fs22\insrsid8340458 Paul:}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 \b\f39\fs22\insrsid15480958\charrsid15480958 \tab }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 \f39\fs22\insrsid15480958\charrsid15480958 It\rquote 
s been argued, quite often, that one of the effects of matrifocal, or matrilineal types of kinship is, they marginalise men.  Did you have that impression there?
