\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 \b\f39\fs22\insrsid8340458 Raymond:}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 \b\f39\fs22\insrsid15480958\charrsid15480958 \tab }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 \f39\fs22\insrsid15480958\charrsid15480958 
Well, the interesting thing is that some people who were intermarried, \'85 were protected by their neighbours, and stayed there.  
And that happened a lot, not just in Windsor Forest, but in other areas, especially up the Demerara River, where there was more of that kind of intermarriage, and they would have vigilante groups preventing violence from occurring in their community.  But
, you know, again, it\rquote s only when you begin to look into family histories in some detail, that you can see the degree.  Like the pundit, the Sanatandam priest in Windsor Forest \'85 (LAUGHS) \'85
 you talked to his wife and you discovered that they had black relatives.  And also, you\rquote d say to her, \'93I see you\rquote re cooking some meat there\'94, you say.   \'93Yeah, he\rquote s not supposed to eat meat, but, you know, he\rquote 
s got to keep up his strength!\'94  So the difference between theory and practice is quite \'85 is quite large.  There w
as a building in Windsor Forest, it was an old slave logee, I guess.  It had tiny little rooms, with upstairs and downstairs, divided into, I don\rquote t know how many \'85  It was one big building, and the people in Windsor Forest called it \'93Noah
\rquote s Ark\'94!  It was actually inhabited by blacks who had come as indentured servants during the 19}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 \f39\fs22\super\insrsid15480958\charrsid15480958 th}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 
\f39\fs22\insrsid15480958\charrsid15480958  century, mainly from Barbados, and their descendants had inherited possession of this building, and they lived there.  And everybody got on
 extremely well.  They all went to the same school.  During the 1960s, when you had racial conflict at the national level, those people were driven out, and that building was burnt down, and it no longer exists.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 \b\f39\fs22\insrsid8340458 Paul:}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 \b\f39\fs22\insrsid15480958\charrsid15480958 \tab }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 \f39\fs22\insrsid15480958\charrsid15480958 
