.  But he had a very high opinion of Janet Jagan, who he thought was a very good organiser.  A lot of people, and I think this is a racist sentiment, a lot of people thought that Janet was the brains behind Jagan.  I don\rquote 
t think that was true at all.  I think she was a competent organiser, you know, she ran her Ministries extremely well.  She was Minister of Education at one time.  But she didn\rquote t have \'85 you never heard her make the kind of oratorical}{
