artment Seminar, and some undergraduate would make some remark, and two days later, he would say, \'93You know, I\rquote ve been thinking about what that student said \'85\'94  Incredible!  No, I h}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 
\f39\fs22\insrsid11159634 ad great respect for Parsons.  }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 \f39\fs22\insrsid15480958\charrsid15480958 And the people here, when I first came, were
