t ignorant of Marx.  Parsons had been a member of Malinowski\rquote s seminar at LSE, and then he had gone on to Germany where he\rquote d done economics.  And I don\rquote t know what your opinion is of }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0\afs22 \ltrch\fcs0 
